metadata.name: Bella Ballerina in the Wardrobe 1
metadata.description:
Self portrait of me, a ballerina and content creator traveling through Rome. I found the most beautiful apartment with stunning furniture to pose with. Shot on Cannon R5 with a single flash light. 

With the purchase of this NFT you also get a printed version if you wish, the chance to be my Patreon and met ups with me if you so wish. You can contact me to organise once purchased via any of my platforms. 

https://linktr.ee/bellaballerina
